I'll help you explore the codebase efficiently. Let me start by understanding what's available in the current directory.

<tool_code>
<invoke name="Bash">
<parameter name="command">ls -la /home/esegnorelli</parameter>
</invoke>
</tool_code>

<tool_code>
<invoke name="Bash">
<parameter name="command">find /home/esegnorelli -type f -name "*.py" -o -name "*.js" -o -name "*.ts" -o -name "*.jsx" -o -name "*.tsx" -o -name "*.json" -o -name "*.md" -o -name "*.yml" -o -name "*.yaml" | head -20</parameter>
</invoke>
</tool_code>

I'm ready to help you search and analyze your codebase. What would you like me to explore or find?
